  "difficultyLevel": 4,
  "lyrics": "It's a blackout, it's a way out, it's the time when you think we're at rest It's a blackout, all the times I do It's a blackout, the thoughts of you, ain't tell you now you wanna roll Take back, dreams from then, take the bottle, yeah, yeah, yeah No, no need to pour it out for you, get it down I need every second of every sip, make it strong I need a blackout without you, I need a blackout So I can't remember how you used to make it drop for me Spend that cash, looking so good, it's ecstasy I'm missing it, I don't wanna remember it all I need a blackout, I need a blackout Every time I think about how you left me here I got no life now, there's no life now Just thinking about that money and taking it away I need you more than you need me, that's what I feel I need you more than you needed me I need a blackout, I need a blackout There's no time to remember it anyway Give me a blackout, and just a blackout What do you got on tab? What drugs you got? What can you give to me today? Cause I don't wanna remember you I don't wanna remember how good you were at night Done all that, did everything right, girl I don't wanna remember all the times you said you were mine That we were forever I need a blackout, I need a fucking blackout For you guys, I can't remember anything but The moments you gave Your sexual warnings Blacked out drunk, I caught you up And you tell me to go get low I'm already low, I wish that you'd ever see me And I don't even know Maybe I'll take you with me this time Maybe I'll fucking take you with me this time But we can't leave me two together",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 23.479999542236328,
      "text": "It's a blackout, it's a way out, it's the time when you think we're at rest It's a blackout, all the times I do",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 36.880001068115234,
      "text": "It's a blackout, the thoughts of you, ain't tell you now you wanna roll",
      "start": 27.239999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 45.47999954223633,
      "text": "Take back, dreams from then, take the bottle, yeah, yeah, yeah",
      "start": 36.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 50.380001068115234,
      "text": "No, no need to pour it out for you, get it down",
      "start": 45.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 55.84000015258789,
      "text": "I need every second of every sip, make it strong",
      "start": 50.380001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 63.7599983215332,
      "text": "I need a blackout without you, I need a blackout",
      "start": 55.900001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 75.76000213623047,
      "text": "So I can't remember how you used to make it drop for me",
      "start": 64.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 84.62000274658203,
      "text": "Spend that cash, looking so good, it's ecstasy",
      "start": 76.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 90.9000015258789,
      "text": "I'm missing it, I don't wanna remember it all",
      "start": 84.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 94.9000015258789,
      "text": "I need a blackout, I need a blackout",
      "start": 90.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 99.66000366210938,
      "text": "Every time I think about how you left me here",
      "start": 94.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 104.13999938964844,
      "text": "I got no life now, there's no life now",
      "start": 99.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 109.16000366210938,
      "text": "Just thinking about that money and taking it away",
      "start": 104.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 117.22000122070312,
      "text": "I need you more than you need me, that's what I feel",
      "start": 109.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 125.31999969482422,
      "text": "I need you more than you needed me",
      "start": 118.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 131.5,
      "text": "I need a blackout, I need a blackout",
      "start": 126.5
    },
    {
      "end": 136.17999267578125,
      "text": "There's no time to remember it anyway",
      "start": 131.5
    },
    {
      "end": 140.66000366210938,
      "text": "Give me a blackout, and just a blackout",
      "start": 136.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 143.67999267578125,
      "text": "What do you got on tab? What drugs you got?",
      "start": 140.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 145.89999389648438,
      "text": "What can you give to me today?",
      "start": 143.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 148.77999877929688,
      "text": "Cause I don't wanna remember you",
      "start": 146.24000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 151.74000549316406,
      "text": "I don't wanna remember how good you were at night",
      "start": 148.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 155.32000732421875,
      "text": "Done all that, did everything right, girl",
      "start": 151.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 161.75999450683594,
      "text": "I don't wanna remember all the times you said you were mine",
      "start": 155.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 163.6999969482422,
      "text": "That we were forever",
      "start": 161.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 169.27999877929688,
      "text": "I need a blackout, I need a fucking blackout",
      "start": 163.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 175.60000610351562,
      "text": "For you guys, I can't remember anything but",
      "start": 169.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 178.25999450683594,
      "text": "The moments you gave",
      "start": 175.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 181.94000244140625,
      "text": "Your sexual warnings",
      "start": 178.5
    },
    {
      "end": 186.6999969482422,
      "text": "Blacked out drunk, I caught you up",
      "start": 182.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 190.72000122070312,
      "text": "And you tell me to go get low",
      "start": 186.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 197.1199951171875,
      "text": "I'm already low, I wish that you'd ever see me",
      "start": 191.32000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 198.9199981689453,
      "text": "And I don't even know",
      "start": 197.1199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 201.72000122070312,
      "text": "Maybe I'll take you with me this time",
      "start": 198.9199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 206.1199951171875,
      "text": "Maybe I'll fucking take you with me this time",
      "start": 202.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 208.6199951171875,
      "text": "But we can't leave me two together",
      "start": 206.1199951171875
    }
  ],
